Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:05.48,first,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Zombie House of Terror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:12.45,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:48.04,Tonari-ep-title-black-2-lines,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Come Down to\N Syoyo Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.83,syoyo,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Come Down to Syoyo Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.96,Tonari-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit class 2-D's Asian Cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.01,Tonari-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Want your fortune told?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:56.98,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.95,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit our house of terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:04.01,zombie,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,1)}Zombie House \Nof Terror
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:04.01,fraud,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,1)}Honest Pricing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.92,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.01,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:04.01,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,We got three customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:07.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:09.27,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.24,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, study bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:17.28,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a step, so please watch your footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.28,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.64,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep talking about shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:25.14,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.41,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This room used to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.78,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... And now, you can \Nsee the former owner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.08,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,walking around in search of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:37.42,love,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Fountain of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:37.42,wish,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Make a Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.42,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this nurse isn't even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.93,boobs,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Boobs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.93,500,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,500 yen to enter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.59,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she dressed like a nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:44.11,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.  Best of luck to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.37,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's starting to tick me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.74,Tonari-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.56,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.09,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.53,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  How'd you like my blood spray?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:11.02,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to pick up chicks now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.00,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,You have to introduce us to some chicks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.13,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Chicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:15.93,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.36,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:25.68,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I lost control of my emotions and yelled at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:30.27,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,In hindsight, there was no reason for me to get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.57,Tonari-flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.23,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But... Haru was so casual about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.52,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,When did I become so indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.08,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be firm in my decision making.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.29,book,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Great People of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.29,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Because my decisions were always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.37,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.30,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I were still alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.13,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,would I be doubting myself like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.34,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I like cultural festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:12.07,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you, Mitsuyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.52,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to, Yuzan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.06,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.20,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not to show your face around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:22.81,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that Haru was up \Nall night working on this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:33.66,donuts,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Red Bean Donuts \N100 yen each
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.63,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can I get two red bean donuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.73,Tonari-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.81,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When I pictured how upset he would be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.20,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if I were to show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.98,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely had to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.25,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't bring me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:41.91,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.34,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:50.84,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:51.69,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.48,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.04,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Me?  I'm on my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:57.98,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.35,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,This school is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.01,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Is he lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.66,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You could have asked someone for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.42,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like asking other people for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.09,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.36,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.55,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.11,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:34.30,Tonari-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.73,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaken-kun, want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.56,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it totally wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:54.45,nagoya,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Nagoya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.42,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to introduce us to some girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.62,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Not a rooster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.03,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.45,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:06:01.46,nagoya,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Nagoya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.83,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.70,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of creeps in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.46,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,So I made this to keep people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.27,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I named it Mizutani Shizu—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.21,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use my name for that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.12,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.93,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.33,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He got lost behind the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.68,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.31,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, Sasayan-kun needs you to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.15,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you with Yamaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.69,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Co-Coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.44,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you look me in the eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.44,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.24,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so forceful with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.62,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,It's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.20,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.18,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's play pretend-Zelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.31,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  Wait a sec, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.04,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I get to go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.58,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You told me not to touch you without permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.44,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you say anything to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:36.97,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.93,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Er, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.21,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.98,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't mind my touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.46,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,but she can't stand yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.53,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.55,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.01,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!  Haru just socked the study bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.01,Tonari-overlap,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,That was brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.44,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.  My bad, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.63,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.55,Tonari-internaloverlap,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Say you're sorry, Haru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.49,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? You're out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.06,Tonari-internaloverlap,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You need to say you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.60,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.06,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You're gonna blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.32,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.03,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.42,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.99,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,stay two meters away from me at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.82,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.02,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.75,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.51,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't mean to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.98,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:29.76,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.39,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I just think it's stupid to let him influence my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:39.15,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a spoiled child:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.85,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,arrogant and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.99,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,So why can't I break free of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.97,Tonari-internal/narrator,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is she asking me for advice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.17,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you know what they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.32,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't end a relationship that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.16,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's always looking for that best-of-only-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:04.42,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru is fixated on me because \Nhe doesn't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.36,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:11.61,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to be someone \Nwho was easily accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:17.43,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mitty, you don't trust Haru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:21.70,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:26.45,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It only makes sense to care\N about the people you're closest to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:31.44,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel the same way about Haru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.07,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.03,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But Natsume-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.82,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.23,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,That study bug is so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:56.26,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because Yamaken had to provoke Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:57.61,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.64,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,How is this my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.64,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't we go comfort her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.64,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:12.00,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mitty, you don't trust Haru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.74,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.16,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.01,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.33,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the blame for \Nwhat happened to your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.72,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It was clearly your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.99,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.92,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Haru's all alone again after pissing you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.53,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.12,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to tell you why \Nyou can't break free of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:38.80,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.45,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the expectations you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:44.55,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Because his words and actions \Nfulfill some of your own hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.31,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't break free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.07,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,You want him to meet your expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.10,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,but you never meet his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.82,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel, Mizutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.57,final,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1500)}Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.12,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse to give me my \Npersonal space, I can't be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.10,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.80,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hurt them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:13.88,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.09,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling lonely after \Nchasing everyone else off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.93,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Except that I've always been alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.40,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,and I've never felt lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.14,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.60,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,You can't feel lonely if \Nthere's no one else around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.22,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.33,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:40.90,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:44.77,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzan-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:45.91,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.38,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.95,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Yuzan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.87,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.05,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.95,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.47,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You know Yuzan-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.98,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Both brothers used to go to Kaimei Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.71,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.11,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared of Yuzan-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.70,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.86,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.20,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a traumatic experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.62,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Your pride will be your undoing, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.46,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.01,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaken-kun, get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.34,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be clear, I don't feel \Neven an itch for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.42,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:42.69,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.35,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.60,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.71,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.56,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yo-Yoshida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.19,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.98,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That slimeball didn't keep his promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.56,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Er, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.47,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the slimy hair\N person you mentioned before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.65,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Man, today just sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.82,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.94,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be unhappy\N if I said that I like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.63,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.54,Tonari-internal/narrator,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.97,Tonari-internal/narrator,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:35.58,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I tell Shizuku how\N I feel, things only get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.36,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have to resort to force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.04,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.15,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,You keep telling her how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.99,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.90,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to say \Nabout that, Mizutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.58,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.94,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:57.27,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,If I told you that I like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.59,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.72,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.68,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're pretty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.23,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.84,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,but that wasn't what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:16.90,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,I meant that in a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.77,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,...female attracted to male kind of way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:23.56,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.65,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.61,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.54,Tonari-overlap,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,No, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.58,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't be listening to this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.58,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.41,Tonari-overlap,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking something more platonic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.80,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:32.64,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.56,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.67,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.64,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.57,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to give Shizuku-chan some advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.35,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,but she gave you the cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.56,Tonari-flashback,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru is fixated on me because\N he doesn't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:03.36,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like she was reading my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:08.33,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,so I came out a little accusatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.85,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time she'd \Never confided in me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.14,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But you were angry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.94,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong with throwing a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.13,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,If girls get in a fight,\N it's over between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.38,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume Asako is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:29.55,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.35,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It comes down to how badly \Nyou want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.18,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.62,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's the first friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.20,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to let her get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.84,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.09,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:49.02,spunky,,0000,0000,0000,,Spunky Zombie House
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.23,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not going to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.57,Tonari-overlap,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.74,Tonari-overlap,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Natsume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.02,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.78,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.85,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.08,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, baseball boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.74,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.70,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.50,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm with Yuzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.71,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.18,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:14.53,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We have an audience now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.31,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.52,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.58,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to cause another scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:37.75,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, are you really willing to hurt that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.46,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.01,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.24,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Oshima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.27,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.  Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.64,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.32,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You're brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.27,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:11.07,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-chan, I wanted to—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.15,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.78,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,She's busy showing me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.87,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:24.07,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the Yamaguchis' son, Kenji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.65,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're all grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.57,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Shizuku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.21,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haru left his shoes behind when he ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:33.45,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give these to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.72,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you back to your classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.14,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.03,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you forgot part of your costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.60,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.00,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you around, Shizuku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.55,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.61,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.18,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with the study bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.60,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.49,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.56,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Smells fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.56,Tonari-overlap,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Mizutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:59.77,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Smells fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.32,Tonari-overlap,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.20,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:18.18,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel bad, you should \Nstart thinking before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.81,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.53,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.53,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you need to reflect on your mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.05,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,since you're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.78,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.45,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just as stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.05,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I keep making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.41,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say to stay two meters away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:45.48,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can I take that back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.79,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that it was \Npointless to establish rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.42,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you finally came to your senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.42,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.98,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go apologize to Oshima first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.02,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.00,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've recognized your mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.61,Tonari-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,it's easy enough to correct them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.09,Tonari-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.57,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.18,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You were just trying to offer some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.30,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My reaction was unwarranted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.64,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.13,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.84,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,your friend and Haru-kun's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.74,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.09,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.76,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.32,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.66,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!  There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.66,spunky,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Spunky Zombie House
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.66,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You guys need to get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.21,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about making you wait, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.73,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.79,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.70,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.33,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You scared {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.05,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:03.71,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.97,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to touch your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.36,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  My hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.68,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.01,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You say you don't love me,\N but you act like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.21,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Then you tell me to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.40,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have a chance or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.97,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.46,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.19,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru is always sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.41,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurting my wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:48.01,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't been honest with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.01,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you confront me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.25,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I start wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.96,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,"Why do I feel this way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.94,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,"Am I making the right choices?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.39,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If I make the wrong choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:07.37,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,will I go back to loving you so much, \Nmy grades start suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.78,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to focus on studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.64,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.13,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been up against all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.76,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:24.31,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.29,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be able to concentrate on studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.46,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:33.83,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't study, I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.12,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing, Haru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:41.71,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:42.82,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.24,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.60,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:49.57,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:52.29,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This has happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.78,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:02.96,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up then, I could feel \Nthe warmth of another human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:06.97,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,A sense of security both \Ncomforting and heartrending.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.43,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I didn't understand \Nwhat this feeling was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.02,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:19.27,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you give me a little more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.52,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think about our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:25.27,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.17,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,myself, and Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:32.33,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The rest comes after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:09.03,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be this adorable little thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:10.98,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but, these days, she just ignores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.98,0:24:14.58,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It must be genetic.  It's in her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.65,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me feel so ordinary.
